WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.560
It was an orthodox religious establishment.

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:14.240
Every member could read, of course, fluent Hebrew, and we conducted the services, very,

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:16.680
very, very lovely services.

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:26.240
And they discovered I had a fairly good voice, and very often I was taken to lead the services

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:31.200
there, which I found uplifted.

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:31.840
That's the right word.

